  "title": "Quantity Surveyor (M&E tender)",
  "description": "<h2><u>Quantity Surveyor (M&amp;E tender)</u></h2>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Descriptions:<br>\n<br>\nReporting to the Manager, you will be responsible for the following duties:<br>\nProvide administration support to QS Department.<br>\nPrepare BQ and costing for project Tender Submission.<br>\nUnderstanding of Tenders with respect to scope of work, pricing schedule and non-material requirements.<br>\nOther ad-hoc duties assigned by the Manager.<br>\n<br>\nJob Requirements:<br>\n<br>\nNTC / Diploma Holder in Electrical and/or Mechanical Works<br>\nMinimum 2 to 3 years of Project Tendering experience.<br>\nAble to work independently.<br>\nKnowledge in MS Office Applications (Word, Excel &amp; PowerPoint).</p>",
